"ogimage":"http://s3-media4.ak.yelpcdn.com/bphoto/Flf8QfqlTJOlAj8RDMyW_Q/l.jpg",
"rating":"4.0",
"reviewcomment":"Came here with a group of about 20 family members. Wasn&#39;t sure what to expect, but this was the one of the most fun dining experiences I&#39;ve ever had! The restaurant isn&#39;t fancy but as soon as you walk in, you&#39;re treated like family.<br><br>We did the family style plan where you pay one price per person for unlimited food/wine/sangria. Totally worth it! They bring out plate after plate after plate of delicious food. Fresh mozzarella, pizza, seafood platters, homemade pasta, lamb chops, steaks, crab, lobster, shrimp....unbelievable.<br><br>The entertainment makes the experience, too -- usually about every half hour, the entire restaurant would bust out in song, swinging napkins over their heads to sing the birthday song. The wine continues flowing and then the dessert platters roll out. The Nutella crepes were awesome! I can&#39;t wait to go back here.",
